Class IDataParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.util.coder.IDataCoder
      • permafrost.tundra.data.IDataParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IDataCSVParser, IDataExcelParser, IDataHjsonParser, IDataHTMLParser, IDataJSONParser, IDataPropertiesParser, IDataXMLParser, IDataYAMLParser

    public abstract class IDataParser
extends com.wm.util.coder.IDataCoder
    Provides a base implementation of an IDataParser class, and a bridge to an IDataCoder class.
